1. *Avionom* putujemo za Pariz. (We are traveling to Paris by *plane*.) 
2. Ne volim da putujem *avionom*. (I don't like to travel by *plane*.)
3. Čekali smo *avionom* satima. (We waited for the *plane* for hours.)
4. Kupila sam kartu za let *avionom*. (I bought a ticket for a *plane* flight.)
5. *Avionom* je najbrži način putovanja. (Traveling by *plane* is the fastest way.)
6. Pilot je spreman za polazak *avionom*. (The pilot is ready for takeoff by *plane*.)
7. Svake godine putujem *avionom* na more. (Every year I travel by *plane* to the seaside.)
8. Čuli smo zvuk *aviona* koji nadlijeće našu kuću. (We heard the sound of a *plane* flying over our house.) 
9. Stjuardese su nasljedile uniforme od bivše *avio-kompanije*. (The flight attendants inherited uniforms from the former *airline* company.)
10. *Avionom* su prevezli pomoć ugroženom području. (They transported aid to the affected area by *plane*.)